com.romanostrechlis.rssnews.content

Class RssFeed

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.romanostrechlis.rssnews.content.RssFeed

  • public class RssFeed
extends Object
    Represents an RSS link.

    It has String attributes id, name, url, category, content and holds a Collection and a List of RssItems.

    Constructors

    • RssFeed(String, String, String, String): Used to add new RSS feeds to application.
